 F_X(z) = P[X\leq{}z] = P[(Y - \alpha)/\beta \leq{}z] = P[Y - \alpha \leq{}z\beta] = P[Y \leq{}(z\beta) + \alpha] = F_Y((z\beta) + \alpha)
